<section class="d-flex align-items-center" aria-label="Hero Section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6 d-lg-flex flex-lg-column justify-content-center align-items-stretch pt-5 pt-lg-0 order-2 order-lg-1" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div>
          <h1>HabitBuddy</h1>
          <h2 class="text-body">Trust the process. Celebrate your progress.</h2>
          <%= link_to 'Sign up today!', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-dark mt-4', role: 'button' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 d-lg-flex flex-lg-column align-items-stretch order-1 order-lg-2" data-aos="fade-up">
        <img src="<%= asset_path 'cuterhippo-chatbubble.png' %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Cute hippo with a chat bubble">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="how-to-use-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="heading mt-5">
      <h2 id="how-to-use-heading">How to use HabitBuddy</h2>
      <h4 class="text-body">It is actually pretty simple.</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="row no-gutters mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-4 box" role="article" aria-labelledby="step-one-heading">
        <img src="<%= asset_path 'number-one.png' %>" alt="Number one icon">
        <h4 id="step-one-heading" class="text-primary">Create an Account</h4>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 box featured" role="article" aria-labelledby="step-two-heading">
        <img src="<%= asset_path 'number-two.png' %>" alt="Number two icon">
        <h4 id="step-two-heading" class="text-primary">Add your Habits</h4>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 box" role="article" aria-labelledby="step-three-heading">
        <img src="<%= asset_path 'number-three.png' %>" alt="Number three icon">
        <h4 id="step-three-heading" class="text-primary">Record Your Progress</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="features-demo-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="heading mt-5">
      <h2 id="features-demo-heading">See HabitBuddy in Action</h2>
      <h4 class="text-body">Watch how HabitBuddy works and explore its features!</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <img src="<%= asset_path 'habitbuddy.gif' %>" alt="Demo of HabitBuddy features" class="img-fluid border-highlight">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="testimonials-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonials-header mt-5">
      <h2 id="testimonials-heading">Testimonials</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials">
      <div class="testimonial-item" role="article" aria-labelledby="testimonial-one-heading">
        <img src="<%= asset_path 'peep-one.png' %>" alt="Araceli H.">
        <h3 id="testimonial-one-heading">Araceli H.</h3>
        <h4 class="text-primary">CEO &amp; Founder</h4>
        <p>
          <i class="bx bxs-quote-alt-left quote-icon-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          I've tried many habit tracker apps, but HabitBuddy stands out with its clean design and intuitive interface. The streak feature gives me a clear picture of my progress!
          <i class="bx bxs-quote-alt-right quote-icon-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-item" role="article" aria-labelledby="testimonial-two-heading">
        <img src="<%= asset_path 'peep-two.png' %>" alt="Lorenzo H.P.">
        <h3 id="testimonial-two-heading">Lorenzo H.P.</h3>
        <h4 class="text-primary">Student</h4>
        <p>
          <i class="bx bxs-quote-alt-left quote-icon-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          As someone who struggles with consistency, HabitBuddy has been a game-changer. I appreciate how it celebrates even the smallest amount of progress to keep people motivated. It's an essential tool for anyone serious about self-improvement.
          <i class="bx bxs-quote-alt-right quote-icon-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-me text-center my-5" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="contact-heading">Contact Me</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out to me!</p>
    <p><strong>Name:</strong> Rebecca Herrera</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:rh7@illinois.edu" aria-label="Send an email to Rebecca Herrera">rh7@illinois.edu</a></p>
  </div>
</section>
